description.narrative: The project development objective is to: (i) restore and strengthen priority, irrigation, electricity, water, and sanitation infrastructure damaged by Tropical Storms Olga and Noel or at risk of damage from future storms, and (ii) strengthen INDRHI s and CDEEE's capacity for future risk management.
